{"tha-ap562:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap562:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap562:0.3":"Upavanattheraapadana ","tha-ap562:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap562:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap562:1.3":"Jalitva aggikkhandhova, ","tha-ap562:1.4":"sambuddho parinibbuto. ","tha-ap562:2.1":"Mahajana samagamma, ","tha-ap562:2.2":"pujayitva tathagatam; ","tha-ap562:2.3":"Citakam katva sugatam, ","tha-ap562:2.4":"sariram abhiropayum. ","tha-ap562:3.1":"Sarirakiccam katvana, ","tha-ap562:3.2":"dhatum tattha samanayum; ","tha-ap562:3.3":"Sadevamanussa sabbe, ","tha-ap562:3.4":"buddhathupam akamsu te. ","tha-ap562:4.1":"Pathama kancanamaya, ","tha-ap562:4.2":"dutiya ca manimaya; ","tha-ap562:4.3":"Tatiya rupiyamaya, ","tha-ap562:4.4":"catutthi phalikamaya. ","tha-ap562:5.1":"Tattha pancamika ceva, ","tha-ap562:5.2":"lohitankamaya ahu; ","tha-ap562:5.3":"Chattha masaragallassa, ","tha-ap562:5.4":"sabbam ratanamayupari. ","tha-ap562:6.1":"Jangha manimaya asi, ","tha-ap562:6.2":"vedika ratanamaya; ","tha-ap562:6.3":"Sabbasonnamayo thupo, ","tha-ap562:6.4":"uddham yojanamuggato. ","tha-ap562:7.1":"Deva tattha samagantva, ","tha-ap562:7.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap562:7.3":"‘Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap562:7.4":"lokanathassa tadino. ","tha-ap562:8.1":"Dhatu avenika natthi, ","tha-ap562:8.2":"sariram ekapinditam; ","tha-ap562:8.3":"Imamhi buddhathupamhi, ","tha-ap562:8.4":"kassama kancukam mayam’. ","tha-ap562:9.1":"Deva sattahi ratnehi, ","tha-ap562:9.2":"annam vaddhesum yojanam; ","tha-ap562:9.3":"Thupo dviyojanubbedho, ","tha-ap562:9.4":"timiram byapahanti so. ","tha-ap562:10.1":"Naga tattha samagantva, ","tha-ap562:10.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap562:10.3":"‘Manussa ceva deva ca, ","tha-ap562:10.4":"buddhathupam akamsu te. ","tha-ap562:11.1":"Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap562:11.2":"appamatta sadevaka; ","tha-ap562:11.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap562:11.4":"lokanathassa tadino’. ","tha-ap562:12.1":"Indanilam mahanilam, ","tha-ap562:12.2":"atho jotirasam manim; ","tha-ap562:12.3":"Ekato sannipatetva, ","tha-ap562:12.4":"buddhathupam achadayum. ","tha-ap562:13.1":"Sabbam manimayam asi, ","tha-ap562:13.2":"yavata buddhacetiyam; ","tha-ap562:13.3":"Tiyojanasamubbedham, ","tha-ap562:13.4":"alokakaranam tada. ","tha-ap562:14.1":"Garula ca samagantva, ","tha-ap562:14.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap562:14.3":"‘Manussa devanaga ca, ","tha-ap562:14.4":"buddhapujam akamsu te. ","tha-ap562:15.1":"Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap562:15.2":"appamatta sadevaka; ","tha-ap562:15.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap562:15.4":"lokanathassa tadino’. ","tha-ap562:16.1":"Sabbam manimayam thupam, ","tha-ap562:16.2":"akarum te ca kancukam; ","tha-ap562:16.3":"Yojanam tepi vaddhesum, ","tha-ap562:16.4":"ayatam buddhacetiyam. ","tha-ap562:17.1":"Catuyojanamubbedho, ","tha-ap562:17.2":"buddhathupo virocati; ","tha-ap562:17.3":"Obhaseti disa sabba, ","tha-ap562:17.4":"sataramsiva uggato. ","tha-ap562:18.1":"Kumbhanda ca samagantva, ","tha-ap562:18.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap562:18.3":"‘Manussa ceva deva ca, ","tha-ap562:18.4":"naga ca garula tatha. ","tha-ap562:19.1":"Paccekam buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap562:19.2":"akamsu thupamuttamam; ","tha-ap562:19.3":"Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap562:19.4":"appamatta sadevaka. ","tha-ap562:20.1":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap562:20.2":"lokanathassa tadino; ","tha-ap562:20.3":"Ratanehi chadessama, ","tha-ap562:20.4":"ayatam buddhacetiyam’. ","tha-ap562:21.1":"Yojanam tepi vaddhesum, ","tha-ap562:21.2":"ayatam buddhacetiyam; ","tha-ap562:21.3":"Pancayojanamubbedho, ","tha-ap562:21.4":"thupo obhasate tada. ","tha-ap562:22.1":"Yakkha tattha samagantva, ","tha-ap562:22.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap562:22.3":"‘Manussa devanaga ca, ","tha-ap562:22.4":"garula ca kumbhandaka. ","tha-ap562:23.1":"Paccekam buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap562:23.2":"akamsu thupamuttamam; ","tha-ap562:23.3":"Ma no pamatta assumha, ","tha-ap562:23.4":"appamatta sadevaka. ","tha-ap562:24.1":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap562:24.2":"lokanathassa tadino; ","tha-ap562:24.3":"Phalika chadayissama, ","tha-ap562:24.4":"ayatam buddhacetiyam’. ","tha-ap562:25.1":"Yojanam tepi vaddhesum, ","tha-ap562:25.2":"ayatam buddhacetiyam; ","tha-ap562:25.3":"Chayojanikamubbedho, ","tha-ap562:25.4":"thupo obhasate tada. ","tha-ap562:26.1":"Gandhabba ca samagantva, ","tha-ap562:26.2":"ekato mantayum tada; ","tha-ap562:26.3":"‘Manuja devata naga, ","tha-ap562:26.4":"kumbhanda guyhaka tatha. ","tha-ap562:27.1":"Sabbe akamsu buddhathupam, ","tha-ap562:27.2":"mayamettha akaraka; ","tha-ap562:27.3":"Mayampi thupam kassama, ","tha-ap562:27.4":"lokanathassa tadino’. ","tha-ap562:28.1":"Vediyo satta katvana, ","tha-ap562:28.2":"dhajam chattam akamsu te; ","tha-ap562:28.3":"Sabbasonnamayam thupam, ","tha-ap562:28.4":"gandhabba karayum tada. ","tha-ap562:29.1":"Sattayojanamubbedho, ","tha-ap562:29.2":"thupo obhasate tada; ","tha-ap562:29.3":"Rattindiva na nayanti, ","tha-ap562:29.4":"aloko hoti sabbada. ","tha-ap562:30.1":"Abhibhonti na tassabha, ","tha-ap562:30.2":"candasura sataraka; ","tha-ap562:30.3":"Samanta yojanasate, ","tha-ap562:30.4":"padipopi na pajjali. ","tha-ap562:31.1":"Tena kalena ye keci, ","tha-ap562:31.2":"thupam pujenti manusa; ","tha-ap562:31.3":"Na te thupam aruhanti, ","tha-ap562:31.4":"ambare ukkhipanti te. ","tha-ap562:32.1":"Devehi thapito yakkho, ","tha-ap562:32.2":"abhisammatanamako; ","tha-ap562:32.3":"Dhajam va pupphadamam va, ","tha-ap562:32.4":"abhiropeti uttarim. ","tha-ap562:33.1":"Na te passanti tam yakkham, ","tha-ap562:33.2":"damam passanti gacchato; ","tha-ap562:33.3":"Evam passitva gacchanta, ","tha-ap562:33.4":"sabbe gacchanti suggatim. ","tha-ap562:34.1":"Viruddha ye pavacane, ","tha-ap562:34.2":"pasanna ye ca sasane; ","tha-ap562:34.3":"Patihiram datthukama, ","tha-ap562:34.4":"thupam pujenti manusa. ","tha-ap562:35.1":"Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap562:35.2":"ahosim bhatako tada; ","tha-ap562:35.3":"Amoditam janam disva, ","tha-ap562:35.4":"evam cintesaham tada. ","tha-ap562:36.1":"‘Ularo bhagava neso, ","tha-ap562:36.2":"yassa dhatughare disam; ","tha-ap562:36.3":"Ima ca janata tuttha, ","tha-ap562:36.4":"karam kubbam na tappare. ","tha-ap562:37.1":"Ahampi karam kassami, ","tha-ap562:37.2":"lokanathassa tadino; ","tha-ap562:37.3":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap562:37.4":"bhavissami anagate’. ","tha-ap562:38.1":"Sudhotam rajakenaham, ","tha-ap562:38.2":"uttareyyam patam mama; ","tha-ap562:38.3":"Velagge alaggetvana, ","tha-ap562:38.4":"dhajam ukkhipimambare. ","tha-ap562:39.1":"Abhisammatako gayha, ","tha-ap562:39.2":"ambare hasi me dhajam; ","tha-ap562:39.3":"Vateritam dhajam disva, ","tha-ap562:39.4":"bhiyyo hasam janesaham. ","tha-ap562:40.1":"Tattha cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap562:40.2":"samanam upasankamim; ","tha-ap562:40.3":"Tam bhikkhum abhivadetva, ","tha-ap562:40.4":"vipakam pucchaham dhaje. ","tha-ap562:41.1":"So me kathesi anandi, ","tha-ap562:41.2":"pitisanjananam mama; ","tha-ap562:41.3":"‘Tassa dhajassa vipakam, ","tha-ap562:41.4":"anubhossasi sabbada. ","tha-ap562:42.1":"Hatthiassarathapatti, ","tha-ap562:42.2":"sena ca caturangini; ","tha-ap562:42.3":"Parivaressanti tam niccam, ","tha-ap562:42.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap562:43.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap562:43.2":"bheriyo samalankata; ","tha-ap562:43.3":"Parivaressanti tam niccam, ","tha-ap562:43.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap562:44.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap562:44.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap562:44.3":"Vicittavatthabharana, ","tha-ap562:44.4":"amukkamanikundala. ","tha-ap562:45.1":"Alarapamha hasula, ","tha-ap562:45.2":"susanna tanumajjhima; ","tha-ap562:45.3":"Parivaressanti tam niccam, ","tha-ap562:45.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap562:46.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap562:46.2":"devaloke ramissasi; ","tha-ap562:46.3":"Asitikkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap562:46.4":"devarajjam karissasi. ","tha-ap562:47.1":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap562:47.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap562:47.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap562:47.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap562:48.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap562:48.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap562:48.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap562:48.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap562:49.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap562:49.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap562:49.3":"Punnakammena sannutto, ","tha-ap562:49.4":"brahmabandhu bhavissasi. ","tha-ap562:50.1":"Asitikotim chaddetva, ","tha-ap562:50.2":"dase kammakare bahu; ","tha-ap562:50.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap562:50.4":"sasane pabbajissasi. ","tha-ap562:51.1":"Aradhayitva sambuddham, ","tha-ap562:51.2":"gotamam sakyapungavam; ","tha-ap562:51.3":"Upavanoti namena, ","tha-ap562:51.4":"hessasi satthu savako’. ","tha-ap562:52.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap562:52.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap562:52.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap562:52.4":"kilese jhapayim mama. ","tha-ap562:53.1":"Cakkavattissa santassa, ","tha-ap562:53.2":"catuddipissarassa me; ","tha-ap562:53.3":"Tini yojanani samanta, ","tha-ap562:53.4":"ussiyanti dhaja sada. ","tha-ap562:54.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap562:54.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap562:54.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap562:54.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap562:55.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap562:55.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap562:55.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap562:56.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap562:56.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap562:56.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap562:57.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap562:57.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap562:57.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap562:58.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upavanatthero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap562:59.1":"Upavanattherassapadanam dasamam. "}